70
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,240
One that's a huge problem now

71
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:40,320
is all the subscription services.

72
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:42,820
You know, like your cell phone, Netflix,

73
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:45,970
and even those mystery
boxes we all sign up for.

74
00:02:45,970 --> 00:02:47,550
Now, we sign up for these things

75
00:02:47,550 --> 00:02:49,130
and then we never cancel them.

76
00:02:49,130 --> 00:02:52,010
And every month they leach
off our bank accounts

77
00:02:52,010 --> 00:02:53,490
even if we don't use them.

78
00:02:53,490 --> 00:02:56,420
By tracking everything it
gives you a much better idea

79
00:02:56,420 --> 00:02:58,500
of your financial situation.

80
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:00,830
Once you, where your money's going

81
00:03:00,830 --> 00:03:03,880
it's actually much easier
to take control of it.

82
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,040
With this information,

83
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:07,020
I was able to take the next step

84
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:08,630
and set some targets.

85
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:11,630
Without a target it's very,
very hard to save any money

86
00:03:11,630 --> 00:03:14,480
because as soon as something
shiny and new comes along

87
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:16,300
you end up blowing all your money

88
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:18,330
and having to restart from zero.

89
00:03:18,330 --> 00:03:21,140
A target gives you a direction
and helps you to resist

90
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:23,820
all those personalized ads on social media

91
00:03:23,820 --> 00:03:26,850
that are trying to separate
you from your hard-earned cash.

92
00:03:26,850 --> 00:03:28,750
I first had a year-long vision

93
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:31,860
which was to be entirely
debt-free by the end of the year.

94
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:34,040
But I knew if I was going to achieve that

95
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:37,210
I needed to break it down
into manageable steps.

96
00:03:37,210 --> 00:03:39,770
When I started working
backwards from my vision

97
00:03:39,770 --> 00:03:42,500
