to cut down on food costs.

191
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:15,340
So I started cooking at
home instead of going out.

192
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:17,810
I was able to make meals
last two or three days,

193
00:07:17,810 --> 00:07:18,650
which was great.

194
00:07:18,650 --> 00:07:21,270
I reduced my monthly bills
by turning off the lights

195
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:23,060
