I didn't need them on.

196
00:07:23,060 --> 00:07:25,350
This may seem like something really small

197
00:07:25,350 --> 00:07:27,800
but it all added up, especially back then.

198
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:30,750
For my travel I considered a few option.

199
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:32,220
I could use public transport,

200
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:35,340
which is a lot cheaper than a
car, but it wasn't practical

201
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:38,760
