221
00:08:24,770 --> 00:08:27,560
This means they were both
made in the same factory

222
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:30,080
but it had a $3 difference.

223
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,430
This is just one example

224
00:08:31,430 --> 00:08:33,930
