scammed by the branding.

225
00:08:33,930 --> 00:08:36,360
I don't know about you,
but every now and again

226
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:39,070
I get the urge to spend a
little bit of money on myself

227
00:08:39,070 --> 00:08:42,250
